                        Git becomes efficient external memory for AI agents. Through epistemic self-awareness, your AI automatically maps every decision, uncertainty, and capability shift to git notes‚Äîturning your repository into a distributed cognitive state machine. No manual tracking, no context loss, just seamless version-controlled reasoning.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- WHAT Section -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">What Is Empirica?</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Three core capabilities that make AI agents smarter, more reliable, and easier to coordinate.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bento-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));">
            <!-- Mirror Drift Detection -->
            <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-xl glow-effect">
                <div class="text-5xl mb-4">ü™û</div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-400 mb-4">Mirror Drift Detection</h3>
