                </p>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 border-l-2 border-cyan-500 pl-4">
                    <strong class="text-cyan-300">How:</strong> Epistemic handoff reports (238 tokens) + git checkpoints. 98% token reduction vs. full context replay.
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Git-Native Coordination -->
            <div class="glass-card p-8 rounded-xl glow-effect">
                <div class="text-5xl mb-4">üå≥</div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-4">Git-Native Coordination</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                    Your repository is the source of truth. Epistemic checkpoints stored in git notes‚Äîdistributed, version-controlled, queryable. Multi-agent coordination without central servers.
                </p>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 border-l-2 border-green-500 pl-4">
                    <strong class="text-green-300">How:</strong> Triple storage (SQLite + Git + JSON). Checkpoint discovery, branch-based workflows, crypto-ready.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- WHY Section -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20">
